{"tid":2443822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"69歲男子接種科興疫苗後面癱　衛生署：需更多臨牀資料病歷作評估","createTime":"2021-03-12T09:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:02:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"a84ef61709c2aff9f2f35455ea7b4f6a0a38cf5f","tid":2443822,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"一名69歲男子接種科興兩小時後眼部不適，送院診斷為貝爾面癱。衛生署公布，該男子於3月6日中午近1時在中央圖書館展覽廳疫苗接種中心接種科興疫苗，約兩小時後左眼不適，不能完全合上左眼；3月7日左邊口流口水，左眼無淚水，他到律敦治醫院急症室求醫，初步診斷為貝爾面癱，並於3月8日出院。<br />\n<br />\n衛生署助理署長（藥物）陳凌峯表示，至今只錄得上述一宗面癱個案，新冠疫苗臨牀事件專家委員會初步討論過有關個案，但需要更多臨牀資料後進行因果關係評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210312/s00001/1615540723769/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e7%96%ab%e8%8b%97-69%e6%ad%b2%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e6%8e%a5%e7%a8%ae%e7%a7%91%e8%88%88%e7%96%ab%e8%8b%97%e5%be%8c%e9%9d%a2%e7%99%b1-%e8%a1%9b%e7%94%9f%e7%bd%b2-%e9%9c%80%e6%9b%b4%e5%a4%9a%e8%87%a8%e7%89%80%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99%e7%97%85%e6%ad%b7%e4%bd%9c%e8%a9%95%e4%bc%b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210312%2Fs00001%2F1615540723769%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e7%2596%25ab%25e8%258b%2597-69%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e7%2594%25b7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e6%258e%25a5%25e7%25a8%25ae%25e7%25a7%2591%25e8%2588%2588%25e7%2596%25ab%25e8%258b%2597%25e5%25be%258c%25e9%259d%25a2%25e7%2599%25b1-%25e8%25a1%259b%25e7%2594%259f%25e7%25bd%25b2-%25e9%259c%2580%25e6%259b%25b4%25e5%25a4%259a%25e8%2587%25a8%25e7%2589%2580%25e8%25b3%2587%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%2597%2585%25e6%25ad%25b7%25e4%25bd%259c%25e8%25a9%2595%25e4%25bc%25b0&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgwxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=e4bc9531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210312%2Fs00001%2F1615540723769%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e7%2596%25ab%25e8%258b%2597-69%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e7%2594%25b7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e6%258e%25a5%25e7%25a8%2